headline: PSEG Declares Regular Quarterly Dividend for the Third Quarter of 2025
summary: The Board of Directors of Public Service Enterprise Group (NYSE: PEG) today declared a $0.63 per share dividend on the outstanding common stock of the company for the third quarter of 2025.
